{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">AstroBrawl is a <strong>fast-paced interplanetary shooter</strong> in which gravity is your best ally and your worst enemy. Be an alien warrior through couch/online deathmatch and survival modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/fast_paced.gif?t=1740146481\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udff9 Gravity: Use the planets' gravitational forces to strategically guide your projectiles through space!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/gravity.gif?t=1740146481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\ude80 Versatile Arsenal: Unleash chaos with a variety of weapons and power up's, including bows, rocket launchers, shockwaves, optic camouflage, triple shots,  and even your own body for dashing and stomping. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/Stomp.gif?t=1740146481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/bum_bloque.gif?t=1740146481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcaa Parry mechanics: Why not?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/parry.gif?t=1740146481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf0c Interactive Environments: Explore diverse galaxies, each with its own unique characteristics. Planets can also explode affecting the whole system of forces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/extras/ice_meteor.gif?t=1740146481\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfae Couch/Online gameplay: Enjoy deathmatches and our new survival mode packed with 100 enemy waves. Think you can beat it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfae Cross-Platform: AstroBrawl supports both PC and Android, allowing you to challenge friends across different devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Prepare for fast-paced interplanetary combat, </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play ASTROBRAWL Now!</strong></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3175020?t=1740146481","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3175020?t=1740146481","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/829ea68b00b766cef0475c9faadc9afc8d70fb5f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740146481","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175020/829ea68b00b766cef0475c9faadc9afc8d70fb5f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740146481","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3369310,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">AstroBrawl is a <strong>fast-paced interplanetary shooter</s